            <thetext>Under QNX Neutrino (a flavor of Unix), which has no &lt;sysexits.h&gt; file, the 
default is to assume that include/exits.h exists in the distribution.  But it 
does not.

The workaround that has led to a successful build is simply to make a symbolic 
link from exits.h in include to the lib/sysexits.h file in your Cyrus imapd 
distribution.

   dB</thetext>
